{"tid":190940,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"認真覺得生命冇希望，返工俾車撞","createTime":"2017-04-07T12:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T16:47:38.000Z","uid":98542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3482a8cd55d096a2222692fc68a07727b1a35099","tid":190940,"uid":98542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T12:46:46.000Z","msg":"真心唔想做人<br />\n你話我尻叫又好咩都好<br />\n真係覺得好攰<br />\nFriend又冇乜邊個係真心，又讀唔到書<br />\n成日就好似件廢物咁咩都做唔到<br />\n拍拖仲衰<br />\n次次拍親唔夠一個月就散<br />\n仲要D女仔frd次次都話「睇你個樣唔似冇女追喎」<br />\n屌你有女就唔會搵你吹水喇<br />\n老豆老母又唔駛我養<br />\n成日就出街周圍蒲<br />\n而我就日日hea係屋企打機<br />\n我打CoD打到認Captain Price做老豆都得喇屌<br />\n我都唔想咁頹，但我冇得揀<br />\n我真心唔想繼續做人<br />\n完喇，好嗎？"},{"pid":"bd28f41d06612c90bdb05f7ef01ab2ed90fee27d","tid":190940,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T12:49:03.000Z","msg":"押韻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b7b37a9b95a248c375e5f1b38cb1ade39a132eb","tid":190940,"uid":30999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T12:50:26.000Z","msg":"起碼兩老唔駛養<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cabd94b5972e4916556b0b6866f2232f61a770fe","tid":190940,"uid":98542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T12:56:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>起碼兩老唔駛養<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n更加好，早死早著"},{"pid":"29de469e9250209ec2ef24fdfa5e13689c86310f","tid":190940,"uid":88190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:28:28.000Z","msg":"巴打又唔洗咁灰咼<br />\n得閒咪去發掘下其他興趣，識下其他唔同範疇既人，梗有一個半個可以交心既，未遇到啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a0a3ddadabd758f5b3af40e917f23415a927010","tid":190940,"uid":7267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:35:32.000Z","msg":"同你一樣 差在未想死住<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7106f29b4b306530f515489e0e724b278c958e81","tid":1